## Callouts

> [!NOTE]
> Strict GitHub form.

> [!summary] Aliased to abstract
> Body line.

> [!danger]- Foldable with a title
> Body line.

> [!custom] Unknown defaults to note
> Body line.

> A plain quote, not a callout.

 ---

(heading H2 @0..12
  "Callouts")
(blockquote Some(Note) None @13..45
  (paragraph @25..45
    "Strict GitHub form."))
(blockquote Some(Abstract) Some("Aliased to abstract") @46..92
  (paragraph @48..92
    "Body line."))
(blockquote Some(Danger) Some("Foldable with a title") @93..141
  (paragraph @95..141
    "Body line."))
(blockquote Some(Note) Some("Unknown defaults to note") @142..192
  (paragraph @144..192
    "Body line."))
(blockquote None None @193..225
  (paragraph @195..225
    "A plain quote, not a callout."))
